dataIdInfo.idAbs: This line data layer represents roads for Fond du Lac County, Wisconsin in 2014. It is a feature class within the geodatabase Fond_du_Lac_Roads_2014.gdb. [The roads layer depicts road centerlines for roads in Fond du Lac County, Wisconsin.]
dataIdInfo.idPurp:
This layer is intended for basic applications such as viewing, querying, and map output production, or to provide a basemap to support graphical overlays and analysis with other spatial data.
[The roads layer depicts road centerlines and address ranges for roads in Fond du Lac County, Wisconsin.]
